13
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,400
Great.

14
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,319
Young Master Xu.

15
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:08,919
I want to ask you something.

16
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:11,759
Okay.

17
