Don't be rude.

43
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,839
Miss Linglong.

44
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:04,240
I apologize on behalf of Zi Su.

45
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:05,879
Zi Su

46
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,959
I'm taking Miss Linglong to meet my brother.

47
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,720
But I want to be with you.

48
00:06:09,839 --> 00:06:10,560
Maybe next time.

49
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,199
Miss Linglong.

50
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,240
Brother.

51
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,040
Changqing, you.

52
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:43,399
Brother, let me introduce you, this is Linglong.

53
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:48,600
She is my friend.

54
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,120
Miss Linglong.

55
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:56,439
This is my brother, he is the leader of our Merfolk Tribe.

56
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,360
Nice to meet you, tribal leader.

57
00:06:58,519 --> 00:06:59,560
No need for formalities.

58
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,399
You guys...

59
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,360
We are twins.

60
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:13,079
Recently, Merfolk's Shore has been unstable.

61
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:15,360
Didn't I tell you not to wander around?

62
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:18,560
How could you bring a stranger here?

63
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,600
Brother.

64
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:23,040
Miss Linglong is not a malicious stranger.

65
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:27,079
Besides, I was attacked just now, and she saved me.

66
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:29,680
Attacked? Where? Were you hurt?

67
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:32,639
I'm fine, see.

68
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:33,800
Who attacked you?

69
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:34,800
Well

70
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,560
I was about to tell you about this.

71
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:41,160
The attackers were merfolks controlled
by an evil spirit in the Lotus Pond.

72
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:46,439
The day of sacrifice is approaching and the
evil spirit is taking advantage of the situation.

73
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:48,680
Come on, let's go check out the forbidden area.

74
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,480
Hold on.

75
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:53,759
Miss Linglong

76
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,560
I still have something to deal with my brother.

77
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:58,600
You have a rest first. I'll have someone
prepare some tea snacks for you.

78
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,879
What we were talking about just now...

79
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,319
About that.

80
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:06,519
Wait for me to finish my tasks and I will inquire for you.

81
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,120
Be careful, young master.

82
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,000
Let's go.

83
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:06,080
Don't worry, the barrier is still there
